            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very bad experience. While taking admission to my kid school had given so many false commitment but at the end of July they couldn't give a simple campus to kids . There is only marketing and money making Machine. In July they are offering parents that you can withdraw admission when all renown school admission has been closed. I withdraw my admission in June 20 at the time of cancellation they told us refund will get in 15 days but in August yet not received refund.\nI request to all parents please join together.",
          "publisher": {
